    "problemStatement": "Abundent Numbers:\n\nWrite a program to find the Abundant numbers (integers) within given range.\n\nDivisor of 12:\n12= 1*12\n12= 3*4\n12= 6*2\n\nSum of Divisors: \n1+3+4+6+2 =16\n\n16>12 \n12 is an Abundent Number.",
